Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.26,0:01:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dreams are a sketch - 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.03,0:01:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Onto the monochrome world that we wrote out
