Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll continue to draw out our dreams, full of all our different hopes and wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:02:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the huge skies of this planet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.34,0:02:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}When you add tears to your passion, you make the color purple
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.41,0:02:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}Endure past the anxiety and loneliness on days where nothing goes well
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.82,0:02:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,300)}When you add tears to your hope, you make the color green
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.76,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(300,0)}If you're tired, don't be afraid to take a break before setting off again
